    "Table 5 summarizes the core functions required to acquire data from SDNbased patient-centric agent devices.",
    "We also made all the materials with datasets via Hyperledger 1.",
    "For testing purposes, we collected 1000 medical data where 15 doctors \"prescribed 100\" patients with 20 different test cases.",
    "Due to privacy issues, we only collected index numbers from the hospital database.",
    "The proposed model of this article is mainly designed based on two emerging technologies, including SDN and Blockchain with different sensor devices, to heighten the security of the IoMT networks, as depicted in Fig. 3."
